{"tid":1611580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紅館唱歌賀國㷫：10月2日及3日一連兩日喺紅館搞文藝晚會同青年音樂會","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:37:43.000Z","uid":39897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b2fb8f3bd1ee995a212dfa0878d4a5e7f413f69","tid":1611580,"uid":39897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"今年係國慶70周年，「香港同胞慶祝中華人民共和國成立70周年籌備委員會」噚日成立，繼續由全國政協副主席、前特首董建華做執行主席，中華總商會會長蔡冠深做秘書長。沿襲過去4年做法，籌委會於10月2日及3日一連兩日喺紅館搞文藝晚會同青年音樂會，後者以清新、活力為主調，會請啲青少年喜愛嘅香港、內地和海外藝人帶來充滿動感嘅表演。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190712/s00002/1562867629160/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E7%BA%8C%E9%82%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190712%2Fs00002%2F1562867629160%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2582%2580%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=b42868b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190712%2Fs00002%2F1562867629160%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%2582%2580%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA&h=6beaa5f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190712/s00002/1562867629160/%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E7%BA%8C%E9%82%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"5976bf793f17d67a7dd60bae851f7a796bf2b58c","tid":1611580,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.